---
import Layout from "../layouts/BlogPost.astro";
const pageTitle = "About Me";
const pageDescription =
  "Learn more about Iván Amón — Telecom Engineering student at UPM and self-taught software developer.";
---

<Layout
  title={pageTitle}
  description={pageDescription}
  pubDate={new Date()}
  showHeader={false}
>
  <p>
    Hey! I'm Iván Amón, a Software Engineer focused on backend development and
    systems programming.
  </p>
  <p>
    I learn by building. I believe technologies are a means to an end, not the
    end itself. I currently divide my technical focus between constructing
    robust backend architectures (using tools like Laravel and MySQL) and diving
    into low-level systems programming with Rust. I feel at home in Linux
    environments, manage containerized deployments with Docker, and actively
    leverage AI tools like Claude Code to iterate faster and write cleaner code.
  </p>
  <p>
    I balance this hands-on approach with my degree in Telecommunications
    Engineering at UPM. While the university gives me a solid theoretical
    foundation in networking and architectures, its greatest lesson has been
    resilience—the grit to face complex systems, manage frustration when things
    break, and push through until I find the solution.
  </p>
</Layout>
